d by the FDA to accelerate the development and evaluation of an investigational drug that is intended to ', 'MK-3475 , SCH 900475 , lambrolizumab , pembrolizumab', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Biologic therapy (BRM, immunotherapy)', 'monoclonal antibody'),
